# MEMORY.md

Curated long-term knowledge. Cleo loads this into every prompt.
Keep it concise — this costs tokens on every message.

## Signal

- Bot number: +1XXXXXXXXXX
- Formatting: `**bold**`, `_italic_`, `||spoiler||`, `~strikethrough~`, `` `mono` ``

## Notes

Add facts, preferences, and context Cleo should always remember here.
